contacts.name: Himeko
contacts.signature: I can survive without water, but coffee is my lifeblood

200070000.text: Let's make sure we get back to the Express in time for dinner.

200070002.text: We just got a new shipment of fresh supplies. Anything strike your fancy?

200070003.text: Not a picky eater, anything edible strikes my fancy.

200070004.text: Meat! Load me up on meat!

200070005.text: I can't imagine a life without milk tea.

200070007.text: You say you're not picky, and Dan Heng says he's good with whatever... Guess I'll just have to cook whatever I feel like.

200070008.text:

{NICKNAME}: Anything edible
Himeko: The "whatever I feel like" special

200070010.text: You've had a long day, better let your body refuel!

200070013.text: But milk tea doesn't count as a meal... Well, I'll whip something up.
